title: 5/9 - HR 1 - Nordo Hosts, Michelletti in Studio on Wild/NHL Playoffs
description: Nordo in the big chair today before PA returns tomorrow for VOX in the Box. Pat Michelletti joins for the full first hour in studio breaking down what we saw in the Wild's game 4 loss last night in St Louis. The good the bad and the ugly, with Mich.
